### Why Not 98%?

Recovery is impossible when:
- Funds enter mixers (Tornado Cash, Wasabi)
- Funds convert to privacy coins (Monero)
- Funds off-ramp at non-cooperative exchanges
- No transaction hashes provided

We never guarantee 100% recovery. No legitimate firm can.
